{"timestamp":1774432335143,"source_app":"agentic-harness","session_id":"90605a23-2731-4625-bb65-094faff2d2f4","hook_event_type":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_use_id":"toolu_01CfYLggCkvHnY6MAswQ3z1w","payload":{"session_id":"90605a23-2731-4625-bb65-094faff2d2f4","transcript_path":"/Users/auto/.claude/projects/-Users-auto-agentic-harness-apps-mas-trees-7529f35b/90605a23-2731-4625-bb65-094faff2d2f4.jsonl","cwd":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/7529f35b","permission_mode":"bypassPermissions","hook_event_name":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/7529f35b/specs/issue-7529f35b-adw-8-sdlc_planner-increase-plans-page-header-height.md","content":"# Plan: Increase height of plans page header\n\n## Task Description\nIncrease the height of the plans page header (the `merch-card-collection-header` component when used on plans pages). The header currently uses a filter/search height of 44px. Since no exact target height was provided in the issue, increase by approximately 50% \u2014 raising the interactive control height from 44px to 66px and the search min-height from 44px to 66px \u2014 by overriding the relevant CSS custom properties in the plans-specific CSS.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `web-components/src/variants/plans.css.js` \u2014 Main plans CSS; defines `merch-card-collection-header.plans` overrides; **edit** to add height variable overrides\n- `web-components/src/variants/plans-v2.css.js` \u2014 Plans v2 CSS; also contains `merch-card-collection-header.plans`; **edit** to add height variable overrides consistently\n- `web-components/src/merch-card-collection.js` \u2014 Defines default values for `--merch-card-collection-header-filter-height` (44px) and `--merch-card-collection-header-search-min-height` (44px); **read-only reference**\n\n## Step by Step Tasks\n\n### 1. Override header height in plans.css.js\n- In the existing `merch-card-collection-header.plans` rule (around line 256), add two CSS custom property overrides:\n  - `--merch-card-collection-header-filter-height: 66px;`\n  - `--merch-card-collection-header-search-min-height: 66px;`\n- This increases the filter button and search input heights from 44px to ~66px (~50% taller)\n\n### 2. Override header height in plans-v2.css.js\n- In the existing `merch-card-collection-header.plans` rule (around line 480), add the same two CSS custom property overrides:\n  - `--merch-card-collection-header-filter-height: 66px;`\n  - `--merch-card-collection-header-search-min-height: 66px;`\n\n### 3. Verify no layout breakage\n- Confirm child content (search input, filter button, sort button, result count) remains vertically centered within the taller header\n- The existing `align-items: center` on the `#header` grid in `merch-card-collection.js` ensures child elements stay centered\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- `merch-card-collection-header` on plans pages renders taller than the default 44px height\n- Filter button and search input are at least 66px tall on plans pages\n- Child elements (search, filter, result count) remain vertically aligned within the taller header\n- No layout regression on mobile (MOBILE_LANDSCAPE), tablet (TABLET_UP/TABLET_DOWN), or desktop (DESKTOP_UP, LARGE_DESKTOP) breakpoints\n\n## Validation Commands\n- `node --check web-components/src/variants/plans.css.js`\n- `node --check web-components/src/variants/plans-v2.css.js`\n"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CfYLggCkvHnY6MAswQ3z1w"}}
